msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/tbl.md:73"
msgid "`nil` and `false` are treated as falsy. All other Lua values are treated as truthy."
msgstr "`nil` y `false` se tratan como falsy. Todos los demás valores de Lua se tratan como truthy."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/tbl.md:75
msgid "Iteration stops as soon as a truthy result is found."
